Type of Feat: Class
Specifics: The primal fury unleashes a devastating roar of sound which staggers nearby foes within 30 feet. It deals d6 sonic damage for each point of his Constitution modifier and knocks down enemies for one round. Those that make a Fortitude save (DC 19 + your Constitution modifier) take half damage and are simply dazed for one round. This ability has a 6 minute cooldown. At 20th level this ability improves and deals +50% damage. At 30th level this ability improves and cannot be resisted.
Use: Selected.